OL,14,FLittle
OL,16,FAn ITV News investigation has
OL,17,Funcovered extreme cases of customer
OL,18,Fservice failures by British Gas. One
OL,19,Fcustomer received dozens of bills a
OL,20,Fday, more than 300 over a couple of
OL,21,Fmonths.
