OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FThe UK's largest energy supplier,
OL,8,FBritish Gas, is nearing completion of
OL,9,Ftransferring its 7.5 million customers
OL,10,Fonto the New Energy Platform. The firm
OL,11,Fsays its old system reached functional
OL,12,Fcapacity and the migration to the new
OL,13,Fversion will "improve customer
OL,14,Fservice".
OL,16,FBritish Gas claims this has been
OL,17,Fmostly seamless, but ITV News has been
OL,18,Fapproached by dozens of customers who
OL,19,Fsay the process has caused confusion
OL,20,Fand serious billing problems.
