OL,7,FAnn Adams is a former British Gas
OL,8,Fcustomer who told us she has been
OL,9,Fliving in fear of debt collectors
OL,10,Fafter she began receiving incorrect
OL,11,Fbills for over 200 different accounts,
OL,12,Fall addressed to her home.
OL,14,F"I actually couldn't sleep because I
OL,15,Fthought, what am I going to do if
OL,16,Fthere's a knock at the door?", she
OL,17,Fsaid.
