OL,7,FOn the day of our filming with her,
OL,8,Fdozens more bills arrived at Ann's
OL,9,Faddress. They amounted to tens of
OL,10,Fthousands of pounds.
OL,12,FAnn's son-in-law, Shaun Stott has
OL,13,Fspent months trying to contact British
OL,14,FGas and resolve the accounts error.
