OL,4,Cangry customers with multiple bills a
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FAlison was preparing to remortgage her
OL,8,Ffamily home in January when she
OL,9,Fdiscovered her excellent credit score
OL,10,Fhad been demolished by problems with a
OL,11,FBritish Gas direct debit.
OL,13,FShe contacted the firm daily to
OL,14,Fresolve the issue, but due to delays
OL,15,Fin hearing back from customer service,
OL,16,Fshe missed the chance to secure a
OL,17,Fbetter mortgage rate. Alison had to
OL,18,Faccept a loan on a far higher
OL,19,Frepayments, which she says has cost
OL,20,Fher more than #7,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
