OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FAn email exchange with a British Gas
OL,8,Femployee eventually told Alison
OL,9,FGreenough that a billing error on her
OL,10,Fold account "should've left your
OL,11,Fcredit file when the account moved
OL,12,Fover to our new system, but
OL,13,Funfortunately it was readded."
OL,15,FThe result was devastating for Alison
OL,16,Fand her family, who have had to make
OL,17,Fserious financial sacrifices to keep
OL,18,Ftheir home.
