OL,7,F"I really question the ability of
OL,8,FBritish Gas and the team that they've
OL,9,Fgot to carry out these system
OL,10,Fmigrations," she told us.
OL,12,F"British Gas are a multi-billion-pound
OL,13,Forganisation, you would expect that
OL,14,Fthey would have the appropriate checks
OL,15,Fand balances in place to understand if
