OL,7,FDescribing their time at British Gas,
OL,8,Fthe former call handler said: "A lot
OL,9,Fof times you will receive calls from
OL,10,Fcustomers who are saying that before
OL,11,Fthe migration they were in credit,
OL,12,Fafter the migration they had owed
OL,13,Fthousands and thousands of pounds to
OL,14,Fthe business.
OL,16,F"The system does have its benefits,
OL,17,Fbut the concern here is not the new
OL,18,Fsystem. That is not a concern to
OL,19,Fcustomers or to anyone else. The
OL,20,Fconcern is how it's been rolled out."
