OL,7,FThe Energy Ombudsman, an independent
OL,8,Fwatchdog for the energy sector, told
OL,9,FITV News they have "seen complaints
OL,10,Fthat appear to be related to this
OL,11,Fprocess, including consumers having
OL,12,Fdifficulty accessing their online
OL,13,Faccounts, accounts being billed
OL,14,Fincorrectly and problems with some
OL,15,Fsmart meters not being billed on the
OL,16,Fcorrect tariff".
