OL,7,FWe've heard from dozens of angry
OL,8,FBritish Gas customers who have sent us
OL,9,Ftheir stories of poor customer service.
OL,11,FBritish Gas insists that the switch of
OL,12,Faccounts to its new billing system has
OL,13,Fbeen largely seamless and will bring
OL,14,Fimproved service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/22
