OL,3,CNew British Gas billing system leaves
OL,4,Cangry customers with multiple bills a
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FWhat's clear from our investigation is
OL,8,Fthat there are customers who have seen
OL,9,Fnone of the promised improvements.
OL,10,FWorse still, some have been told the
OL,11,Fprocess of migration to the new
OL,12,Fbilling system has been a factor in
OL,13,Ftheir issues.
OL,15,FWe've seen evidence of confusion, as
OL,16,FBritish Gas customer service staff
OL,17,Frefer to issues with the process - but
OL,18,Ftheir comments are later contradicted
OL,19,Fby the company. There is little wonder
OL,20,Fthat these customers are left puzzled
OL,21,Fby what's going on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/22
