OL,7,FBritish Gas has claimed that the new
OL,8,Fbilling platform has improved customer
OL,9,Fsatisfaction. Yet information on its
OL,10,Fwebsite links to a Citizens Advice
OL,11,Fcomparison which ranks British Gas as
OL,12,F14th in a list of 16 suppliers -
OL,13,Freceiving only 2.4 stars out of a
OL,14,Fpossible 5.
OL,16,FMany customers we've spoken to would
OL,17,Fbe surprised that the UK's biggest
OL,18,Fenergy supplier sees any basis for
OL,19,Fpride in this result.
