OL,7,FBritish Gas says it has lots of
OL,8,Fevidence that its customer service is
OL,9,Fgetting better, including getting
OL,10,F"Best Overall Improvement" award from
OL,11,FUswitch and official analysis showing
OL,12,Fan increase in satisfaction from the
OL,13,Findustry watchdog, Ofgem.
OL,15,FBut it's clear they won't be getting
OL,16,Fany awards from the customers we've
OL,17,Fspoken to for our report.
